                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18361212-267-offence-1 t18361212-cd-38"></join>5th of December</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18361212-name-333" type="victimName">
